@index TOC


@node MAIN "SeventhSense 0.14"
@{jcenter}@{b}SeventhSense 0.14@{ub}
@{jleft}


SeventhSense is a program, which can check web pages for updates. It is useful
not only for static sites, but news portals as well, thanks to versatile dates
search system. As an addition future versions of SeventhSense will contain RSS
news feeds reader.


SeventhSense has been written by Grzegorz Kraszewski. Program and drawer icons
have been drawn by Christian Rosentreter.


Please send bugreports to Grzegorz Kraszewski <krashan@teleinfo.pb.bialystok.pl>.


@{" Proceed to table of contents " LINK TOC}

@endnode


